Summary

Feature                     REST                                        SOAP

Protocol                    Architectural style                         Protocol
Communication               HTTP/HTTPS                                  HTTP, SMTP, TCP, etc.
Data Format                 JSON, XML, HTML, etc.                       XML
Stateless/Stateful          Stateless                                   Can be both
Security                    HTTPS, OAuth                                WS-Security, SSL
Performance                 Generally faster, lightweight               Generally slower, heavyweight
Flexibility                 Flexible data formats                       Strict XML format
Use Cases                   Web and mobile applications, public APIs    Enterprise applications, secure transactions